            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>peanut butter</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>tahini paste</strong>&nbsp;and 3 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [6 tbsp]</span><strong> boiled water </strong>in a small bowl&nbsp;with a whisk until smooth</p>\r\n<p>Add the<strong> fresh</strong>&nbsp;<strong>chilli jam</strong>, <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong>,<strong> honey</strong>, <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and<strong> soy sauce sachets</strong> and mix to combine &ndash; this is your <strong>peanut &amp; sesame sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1068.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
